# Apple Store API rules

**Context:** `@docs/architecture_ledger.json`

1. StoreKit 2 + server notifications only — no AI vendor SDKs here.  
2. Validate all webhooks with Apple signed payload verification.  
3. Push gateway notifies iOS when `campaign_automations.current_step = DISPATCHED`.  
4. Never import from `apps/video-ad-factory/`.
